TI  - Can
a Black Phosphorus Schottky Barrier Transistor Be Good Enough?
LA  - eng
JF  - Acs Applied Materials and Interfaces
VL  - 9
IS  - 4
SP  - 3959
EP  - 3966
PY  - 2017
SN  - 19448252, 19448244
