AB  - With the popularization of virtualization and cloud computing applications, Cloud security issues were highlighted, fault detection of virtual network resource is the physical basis of cloud computing security. In this paper, traffic analysis tools have been used to detect network resources faults. The quantum neural network technology based on multilevel transfer function has been adopted, it can use neural network weight tuning algorithm to adapt more hidden layer activation functions, so as to make the input flow feature vector corresponding to different fault space and detect various network resource faults. Simulation results show that compared with traditional network resource fault detection, flow analysis method has better detection resolution.
